Bundled third-party code
=========================

src/hash.h
----------
The function `rpjrt::hash_combine` in src/hash.h is adapted from the 64-bit
specialization `hash_combine_impl<64>::fn` of Boost.ContainerHash
(boost/container_hash/hash.hpp), adapted only to take an already-computed hash
value directly.

